  "labelText": {
    "raw": "The B-12 content is derived by natural fermentation.\n SUGGESTED USAGE: As a dietary supplement, take one lozenge daily. Chew lozenge or hold in mouth until dissolved. Consider taking this product in combination with NOW(R) B-Complex, Folic Acid, B-6 and TMG. Vitamin B-12 (Cyanocobalamin) is a water soluble vitamin necessary for the maintenance of a healthy nervous system and for the metabolic utilization of fats and proteins. Vitamin B-12 is also essential for the synthesis of DNA during cell division and therefore is especially important for rapidly multiplying cells, such as blood cells. In addition, adequate intake of Vitamin B-12, along with Folic Acid and Vitamin B-6, encourages healthy serum homocysteine levels, thereby supporting cardiovascular health. Because Vitamin B-12 is found predominantly in animal products, strict vegetarians are at risk of developing Vitamin B-12 deficiency and may benefit from supplementation.* NOW(R) Vitamin B-12 is vegetarian/ vegan (non-animal derived). *These statements have not been evaluated by the FDA. This product is not intended to diagnose, treat, cure or prevent any disease. ACTUAL\nSIZE NERVOUS SYSTEM HEALTH \u2022 Essential for DNA Synthesis*\n \u2022 with Folic Acid A Dietary Supplement\n Vegetarian Formula GMP QUALITY ASSURED Made in the U.S.A. Contains no salt, wheat, gluten, soy, milk, egg, shellfish or preservatives.\n Vegetarian/Vegan Product.\n Do Not Eat Freshness Packet. Keep in Bottle.\n Store in a cool, dry place. Please Recycle. CODE 0466 V2",
